Nije mu se *nimalo* svidjelo (He didn't like it at all).
Njegov odgovor nije bio *nimalo* uvjerljiv (His answer was not convincing at all).
On nije imao *nimalo* sreće (He had no luck at all).
Nismo se *nimalo* iznenadili (We were not surprised at all).
Nismo očekivali *nimalo* više (We didn't expect anything more).